We implore you to keep their papers and allow us three brothers to challenge them to another competition
What do you think The king of Tarrycart really was muddleheaded when he heard advice from the East he inclined to the East Journey to the West and when he was advised from the West he inclined to the West What sort of competition with them do you propose Teachers of the Nation he asked
