That's good Master said Monkey There's a wineshop there
I'll go and beg you some hot water and find out if anyone sells medicine there and will let you have some medicine to ease your pain Sanzang was very pleased with the suggestion so he whipped the white horse forward and was soon at the gates of the village where he dismounted
An old woman was sitting on a bundle of straw outside the gates twisting hempen thread
Monkey went up to her put his hands together in front of his chest in greeting and said We monks have come from the Great Tang in the East
My master is the Tang Emperor's younger brother and he has a stomachache because he drank some water from a river Which river did you drink from asked the old woman laughing aloud
From the clear river to the East of here replied Monkey
What a laugh chuckled the old woman what a laugh
