This made Monkey so angry that he shouted and bared his teeth at them sending them all scurrying and stumbling inside in terror
Journey to the West Monkey went after them grabbed the old woman and said Boil some water this minute and I'll spare your life My lord said the old woman hot water won't be any use
I can't do anything to help those two with their bellyaches
