I'm dying I'm dying Stop fidgeting brother said Friar Sand with a grin stop fidgeting or else you'll get the umbilical cord in a twist and be ill before the birth The idiot's panic was now worse than ever as with tears in his eyes he held on to Monkey and said Brother ask the old lady where there are midwives with a gentle touch and send for some
