It looked the same throughout the seasons Changeless forever like a dragon
After looking for a long time the Great Sage walked down from the towering peak to find his way through the mountain
Just when he was feeling bewildered a slender young woman came towards him holding a spray of fragrant orchid
The Great Sage slipped behind a grotesque rock and took a good look at her This is what she was like A ravishing beauty to enchant a nation Walking so slowly on her little lotus feet
Journey to the West Her face was like Wang Qiang or the woman of Chu
She was a talking flower Scented jade
The hair was swept down from her coiffure like jadeblue crows The green of her eyes made one think of autumn floods
Her silken skirt showed a glimpse of tiny feet From her turquoise sleeves came long and elegant wrists
