Brothers said Erlang go and ask him up at once The six brothers Kang Zhang Yao Li Guo and Zhi all came out of their camps and said Great Sage our eldest brother has sent us with an invitation for you Monkey went forward paid his respects to them then accompanied them to the top of the mountain where Lord Erlang received him took him by the hand and returned his courtesies Great Sage he said allow me to congratulate you on being rescued from your terrible sufferings and being converted to the Buddhist faith Soon you will have succeeded and will be sitting on your lotus throne Journey to the West I don't deserve your congratulations Monkey replied
