This will ensure that you live for ever The king ordered that the name be changed and a new board hung up that read
NATIONPROTECTING SUBDUED DRAGON MONASTERY FOUNDED BY ROYAL COMMAND He then commanded that a banquet be laid on and sent for painters to paint portraits of the four of them Their names were recorded in the Tower of Five Phoenixes
