Anyone with a weak spleen would throw up at the first sniff
If he goes on and takes the rhubarb and croton seeds he'll be vomiting at one end and having the runs at the other
That'll be no joke You don't know the inside story said Monkey
That horse of ours is no ordinary horse He used to be a dragon in the Western Ocean
If he'll give us some of his piss it'll cure any illness you could have
My only worry is that he might refuse When Pig heard this he went and stood beside the horse who was lying down asleep
