The demon king has made the security precautions even stricter and he won't open the doors
Will you act like a wife to him and lure him in here to sleep so that I can escape and find some other way of rescuing you When the queen heard this she shivered and shook and her hair stood on end as if a spirit were pulling it she was terrified as if her heart was being pounded by a pestle
