He was just like A black bean on a lotus flower A bee resting on a peony blossom A raisin fallen into a hydrangea A black spot on a wild lily stalk
The queen raised her hand and said Holy monk Journey to the West I'm the holy monk transformed Monkey replied
Only then did the queen believe him
When I invite the demon king here what are you going to do she asked
