Spreading his wings the splendid Monkey flew straight to the top of Spring Beauty's head where he pulled out one of his hairs blew a magic breath on it and called Change It turned into a sleep insect that landed lightly on Spring Beauty's face
Now when sleep insects reach a human face they crawl into the nostrils and once they are inside the person goes to sleep
Spring Beauty did indeed start feeling sleepy She could not keep on her feet but swayed about and felt dozy as she hurried to where she had been resting before collapsed head first and fell into a deep sleep
Brother Monkey then jumped down shook himself turned into Spring Beauty's exact likeness and went back round the screen to line up with the others
As the Golden Queen walked into the front part of the palace a little devil saw her and reported to the Evil Star Matcher The queen's here Your Majesty The demon king hurried out of the Flaying Pavilion to greet her
Your Majesty the queen said the smoke and fire have been put out and there's no sign of the thief
