Itching unbearably the demon king put his hands inside his clothing to rub the irritation He caught a few of the lice between his fingers and took them to a lamp for a closer look
When the queen saw them she said mockingly Your Majesty your shirt must be filthy It can't have been washed for ages I expect that's why they're there I've never had insects like these before he said in embarrassment
