Meanwhile the successful imitation Spring Beauty tucked the treasures into her belt and turned back into Monkey
He shook himself took back the sleep insect and headed for the front of the palace where nightsticks and bells sounded together to mark the third watch Splendid Monkey made himself invisible by making a spell with his hands and saying the words of it
Going straight to the gates he saw that they were very firmly locked and bolted so he brought out his goldbanded cudgel pointed it at the door and made unlocking magic The gates swung easily open
