This so alarmed the demons big and small that while some of them barricaded the gates the others went in to report
As soon as the demon king woke up and heard the cacophonous din he got up dressed and emerged from his bedcurtains to ask What's all the shouting about Sir said the kneeling slave girls someone's been shouting and cursing outside the cave half the night
