You don't know what you're talking about I was politely invited to help by the king of Purpuria
He addressed me very respectfully and treated me well I'm a thousand times higher than that king He treated me as if I were his father and mother or a god How can you say I'm acting like a slave
I'll get you you monster for bullying your superiors and trying to push your master around
