You can ring yours so why shouldn't I ring mine What bells have you got the demon king asked
Show me Monkey pinched his iron cudgel to make it into an embroidery needle that he tucked into his ear then brought out the three real treasures from at his waist
Here are my purple gold bells he said to the demon king
