Once he led his men and horses hunting with falcon and hound They came to the Fallen Phoenix Slope where a young peacock and peahen two children of the Buddha's mother in the West the Bodhisattva Maurya Vidya Rani were resting When the king shot with his bow he wounded the cock while the hen died with an arrow still in her
