Journey to the West Do a change to show me said Sanzang and the splendid Great Sage made a spell with his fingers shook himself and turned into a very neat little monk cleareyed finebrowed roundheaded and regular of features
He moved in a most refined way and said nothing vulgar when he opened his mouth
