Sun the Novice he yelled at the top of his voice you have a thundering reputation They tell of how Journey to the West mighty you were outside the Southern Gate of Heaven and at the Hall of Miraculous Mist I'd heard that you've been capturing demons along your way to the Western Heaven But now I see that you're only a very smalltime ape What makes me smalltime Monkey asked
